cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with improving the resilience of deep neural networks through adversarial training. It also involves image classification tasks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, since the paper discusses the vulnerability of DNNs to adversarial attacks, it could also be categorized under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of adversarial examples in training also suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
